description:
Moheiji is a second-year student. He is in the student council and is the head of the general affairs department. He also is a candidate in the next student council president election. He always wears an odd, http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Henohenomoheji [henohenomoheji]-like mask (only Yuuki sees this).
Source: Wiki
name: Tatsumi Moheiji
